                  "y": 335,
                  "fill": "#000000",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": 432,
                  "content": "Dear Valued Guest,\n\nWelcome to the Affordable Luxury Group (ALG), your urban sanctuary in the heart of Kuala Lumpur, where seamless comfort and the warmth of our hospitality create a stay like no other.\n\nOur passion for service and atention to detail are the heart of everything we do from our thoughtfully designed suites at Arte Plus to our exclusive limosine services. Please feel free to reach out to any member of our team if there is anything we can do to make your experience even more exceptional.\n\nThank you for choosing ALG-Suite. We cannot wait to share our perfect blend of comfort and sophisatication with you.",
